Interface GraphView<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ReadableGraph<T>
    Deprecated. 
    External entities are deprecated. Please use the new Java API instead.

    @Deprecated
public interface GraphView<T>
extends ReadableGraph<T>
    A GraphView is a read-only view on a Graph. Implementations will generally be optimized for multiple read operations (i.e., some "startup cost" but with faster operations).
